name: Agent Aika Style
description:
---V1.0 ---

Lora strength: 1 (0.9 isn't bad either but i didn't test it that much)

Trigger words: RETRO ARTSTYLE, 1990S (STYLE)

prompts to get Aika and Rion(same as v0.1):

Aika: blonde girl, yellow hair, long hair, blue eyes, ponytail

Rion: short hair, red hair, blown eyes, glasses

use Hires. fix for better results

models tested: same as v0.1

what's new in this version:

-more flexibility

-fixed the annoying unwanted generation of "tiled/collaged/magazine page" stuff

-slightly better hands

sometimes the lora will try to do another girl even if "1girl" is in prompt. adding "solo" fixes that.

most of the pictures were made with txt2img->img2img(latent upscale) because I'm a proud owner of a 1060(3gb) and if I use Hires. fix it would take like 15 minutes (1 batch count, 4 batch size), however, i think that Hires. fix gives better results

things to fix in the future:

sometimes, characters are holding stuff

-WARNING-Version 0.1 OLD VERSION

I'm not satisfied with this, its my first style lora. now that I know what I'm doing (kind of) I realize that this has plenty of room for improvements so there will be an update in the future. I'm uploading this anyways because SOMETIMES it works and there could be people interested in it since it was a popular series back in the day.
also, if the hands look good without ControlNet consider playing the lottery.

trigger words: retro artstyle, 1990s (style), anime screencap , screencap

Lora strength: 0.7-1 (with 1 sometimes you will have add weight to some of your prompts)

use Hires. fix for better results

you can summon(most of the time) :

Aika: blonde, ponytail, long hair, blue eyes

Rion: short hair, red hair, blown eyes, glasses

models tested: yesmix_v15, corneos7thHeavenMix_v2, abyssorangemix2_Hard, anything-v4.5, walnutcreamBlend_herbmixV1
